      "para_id": "Q001813.2",
      "line_range": "2",
      "translation": "(1') When he conquered the land of Zabšali and the ( other ) Šimaškian lands , then for ..., ..., the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , fashioned an image of the billy goat brought to him as a diplomatic gift of Anšan . He dedicated it to him for his well-being ."
    }
